column6: With monsters appearing on the utopian island of Arcadia and threatening its inhabitants, She-Hulk and her team of Avengers set out to discover the source. But when they stumble upon a conspiracy that reaches far beyond Arcadia, She-Hulk may just find herself on the wrong side of the law!
column8: | writer:Marguerite Bennett | writer:G. Willow Wilson | penciller (cover):Jorge Molina
